data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER.  Completely remodeled with permits and a certificate of completion.  Move in ready island home awaits your arrival.  Become an islander and be apart of the Fort Myers Beach revitalization.   This elevated 3 bedroom, 2 bath homes sits on a large lot and is ideally located mid island with new everything including, fresh interior paint, updated baths, kitchen with SS appliances and butcher block countertops, plank tile flooring, new ac, hot water heater, complete electrical and re-plumbed, lower paver deck and new gravel drive and front yard.  Offering 2 bedrooms and a full bath upstairs with an open floor plan and large screen balcony.  Utilize the spiral stairs from above or private lower entrance which lead to an efficiency apartment offering a full bath, full kitchen, and separate screened lanai.  Covered parking leads to yet another screened area with paver decking ideal for laundry, extra storage, beach toys or a workshop.  Walk or bike in minutes to the sandy shore.  Come explore all this island home has to offer.
